<tr><td align = left><font color = #394a54 face = "Arial" size = +3><b>March Break at the Library!</b></font><br><br></td></tr>
<tr><td>
<table border = 0 width = 100% align = center><tr>
<td valign = top><img src = ../generalimages/1455823623.png hspace = 10 vspace = 10 border = 0 alt = '' align = left>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<br><font color = # face = "Arial" size = +1>Looking for something fun to do during March Break? Look no further! We have lots of great events for kids happening at every Cumberland Public Libraries location - and they're all free! They fill up fast, so call your local library today to sign up. 
<br>
<br>
Click <A href = index.php?pagecontentid=667&demoid=1&linkid=5>HERE</a> for a full list of events. 
