<tr><td align = left><font color = ##0101D face = "Arial" size = +3><b>FREE family swim pass</b></font><br><br></td></tr>
<tr><td>
<table border = 0 width = 100% align = center><tr>
<td valign = top><img src = ../generalimages/1456933877.jpg hspace = 10 vspace = 10 border = 0 alt = '' align = left>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<br><font color = # face = "Arial" size = +1>Want a chance to get a FREE* family swim pass? <p>
Visit the Four Fathers Library, in Amherst during the month of March for a free family swim pass.<br>
The passes are available on a first come, first served basis and can picked up at the library. They can be used during the $5 family swim times for the specific day you get your pass.<p>
*library card required<br><br>
<br>
<br>
<h3 align="center" class="headerline"> </h3>
</font></td>
